  <div class="row" style="padding-bottom:0px; margin-bottom:20px; border-bottom-style:none; border-block-width:1px; border-color:gainsboro;">
    <div class="col-lg-7">
      <p>
        Explore the wealth of knowledge generated by the ITS Data Program through this curated list of publications. Dive into the world of our publications and discover the cutting-edge
        research and ideas that drive our Program forward.
      </p>
      <p>Note that some documents are currently in the ITS JPO publication process. Once they are available online, hyperlinks will be added to the following lists.</p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://rosap.ntl.bts.gov/" target="_blank">Welcome to ROSA P (bts.gov)</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
